# HKMetadataKeyDateOfEarliestDataUsedForEstimate

**Global Variable**

The earliest date of data used to calculate the sample’s estimated value.

## Declaration

```swift
let HKMetadataKeyDateOfEarliestDataUsedForEstimate: String
```

## Discussion

This key takes a [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/Date] value, indicating the earliest date from the data used by HealthKit to calculate the sample’s value.
